    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices, usually of iron, bent at the ends, or of dovetail form; used to hold together structural timbers or stone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
